{"tid":2501263,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"講下過河遊戲背後既學術","createTime":"2021-04-23T08:45:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T09:42:31.000Z","uid":121095,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bd1117c8d9d993ad4f411d30581714d6b27f2b99","tid":2501263,"uid":121095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:45:27.000Z","msg":"前幾日見到呢個post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2497332/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2497332/page/1</a><br />\n未玩過既可以入去試下玩下<br />\n呢個post主要係講下背後既學術<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點樣搵最短既path / 有無solution<br />\n <br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"violet\">TLDR／懶人包:</span></span></strong><br />\nBFS（廣度優先搜索）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"violet\">預備知識: Graph（圖論）, BFS（廣度優先搜索）</span></span></strong><br />\n識既就可以skip呢part<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"violet\">1. Graph（圖論）</span></span><br />\n<span class=\"violet\">重點：directed graph, cycle</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"violet\"><ins>Directed graph</ins></span><br />\n一個Graph係由Vertex 同 Edge組成<br />\n畫出黎就係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYAWPckSMAj9UFy1BVnBKV6btcJR2jcey7rAF5yPtTEiA?filename=FpPZQF1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFpPZQF1.png&h=3fff67b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nVertex有五粒 分別係 { 0, 1, 2, 3, 4 }<br />\nEdge有五條 分別係 ( 0 -&gt; 1 ) , ( 0 -&gt; 2 ) , ( 2 -&gt; 3 ) , ( 3 -&gt; 4 ) , ( 4 -&gt; 5 )<br />\n<br />\nEdge有箭咀既graph叫做<span class=\"violet\">directed graph</span>，係有方向性既<br />\n無方向既就叫<span class=\"violet\">undirected graph</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmW93YyFLK4MsyTZGiUfsL7pqfLCxhD57oaU9Sdigm9TRc?filename=zTWA8tu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzTWA8tu.png&h=b4b632b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地既主角會係<span class=\"violet\">directed graph </span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"violet\"><ins>Cycle</ins></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYJGyeLukpUvXPnxGsMQajtcBhA722j66BTbQq4RCJBgZ?filename=atVm33a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FatVm33a.png&h=83838551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCycle即係一個循環<br />\n倒如vertex { 2, 3, 4 } 就係一個cycle，因為你可以 2 -&gt; 3 -&gt; 4 -&gt; 2 -&gt; 3 ... 咁樣一路行落去<br />\n{ 0, 1, 2} 就唔係一個cycle<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"violet\"><ins>Graph Traversal</ins></span><br />\n咁有個graph之後，我地想知兩個問題：<br />\n1. Given 兩個vertex {a, b} ，個graph有無一條path係由\ba去到b？<br />\n2. 有既話，最短路徑係邊條<br />\n<br />\n都係睇番呢張圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYJGyeLukpUvXPnxGsMQajtcBhA722j66BTbQq4RCJBgZ?filename=atVm33a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FatVm33a.png&h=83838551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由 0 去 4，有兩條path<br />\n1. 0 -&gt; 1 -&gt; 2 -&gt; 3 -&gt; 4<br />\n2. 0 -&gt; 2 -&gt; 3 -&gt; 4<br />\n所以最短路徑係 0 -&gt; 2 -&gt; 3 -&gt; 4<br />\n簡單既graph可以人手睇，但如果咁呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTvAbbjL6FSdj8jSQJV6jxSMtLQWU5YPg8Fo7tScXNq8C?filename=9P0utHg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9P0utHg.png&h=ffb3d5a9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n我地需要電腦幫手，咁就要一個通用既方法（algorithm）話俾電腦知點搵<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"violet\">2. BFS（廣度優先搜索）</span></span><br />\n都係睇番呢張圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYJGyeLukpUvXPnxGsMQajtcBhA722j66BTbQq4RCJBgZ?filename=atVm33a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FatVm33a.png&h=83838551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我地想由vertex 0 出發去行張圖既話，主要有兩種方法，分別係Breadth-first search (BFS) 同Depth-first search(DFS)<br />\n<br />\nBFS就係盡可能分散咁搵哂啲vertex再深入落下，DFS就相反<br />\n睇gif最實際（from wiki）<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"violet\"><ins>BFS</ins></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXLWrBBGysiCEEY4xLs3VZ4rexk59BAvpiFiDmSMTWy9S?filename=hLD4hKL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLD4hKL.gif&h=efcc3632&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"violet\"><ins>DFS</ins></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPZ31E6nFKReBSeQg6Ep6m4WvYfr7rKiUzU9EVHDgpBNH?filename=OkwEQ5x.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOkwEQ5x.gif&h=78732c72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地會用BFS搵shortest path"},{"pid":"f09b135fdbe0d91d6ae5195b8913007ba278e384","tid":2501263,"uid":121095,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:46:38.000Z","msg":"點樣apply落過河遊戲？<br />\n首先，個game有八個人，我地可以每人assign一個number俾佢，括號入面係二進制<br />\n老豆：1 (1)<br />\n老母：2 (10)<br />\n警察：4 (100)<br />\n仔1：8 (1000)<br />\n仔2：16 (10000)<br />\n女1：32 (100000)<br />\n女2：64 (1000000)<br />\n罪犯：128 (10000000)<br />\n<br />\n咁樣assign有個好處<br />\n我地可以用一個數字去代表有咩人係度<br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n3: 老豆＋老母 (3 = 1 + 2) (11 = 1 + 10)<br />\n11: 老豆＋老母＋仔1 (11 = 1 + 2 + 8) (111 = 1 + 10 + 100)<br />\n56: 仔1＋仔2＋女1 (56 = 8 + 16 + 32) (111000 = 1000 + 10000 + 100000)<br />\n255: 所有人都係度 (255 = 1 + 2 + 4 + &hellip; + 128) (11111111 = 1 + 10 + 100 + &hellip; + 10000000)<br />\n<br />\n同一時間，我地亦都可以知道咩人去左對面岸<br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n254: 老豆 (254 = 255 - 1)<br />\n252: 老豆＋老母 ( 252 = 255 - 1 - 2)<br />\n123: 警察＋罪犯 ( 123 = 255 - 128 - 4)<br />\n0: 所有人過哂去，即係爆機！<br />\n<br />\n用graph去表達<br />\n<br />\n一開始255即係全部人都係度，有兩條path<br />\n1. 老豆老母過去 (252)<br />\n2. 警察同犯過去 (123)<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTKkgkbW8Gdf5TVqyXKBoMExhVMAbPwXpo8jC8rhqJG74?filename=ThJsfRD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FThJsfRD.png&h=d26a4bc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果follow (123)條path，黎緊有兩個path<br />\n1. 警察同犯番黎<br />\n2. 警察自己一個番黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRCGYeXHhNFx59ds5gyG4aaXifgGwf63wDknggzGYUNKs?filename=rPToyDm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrPToyDm.png&h=1435b6e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如此類推，目的地就係vertex 0<br />\n用BFS就可以搵到<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQFdPWQZuc43xZQA2yM9K7EhmAXNvMg7bNY91BS9MxRDT?filename=PoxwHwL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPoxwHwL.png&h=b469f6a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e35cd96fc68753234e00085ade722c9da2b0f95","tid":2501263,"uid":101554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:47:42.000Z","msg":"好似勁正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b98e5f1d7de7dffe784b9300e3774b733b3ca24","tid":2501263,"uid":205339,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:50:35.000Z","msg":"痴撚線po"},{"pid":"ef8e6487a1fcd63021758c25f9b62b4713739149","tid":2501263,"uid":101554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:53:15.000Z","msg":"256 nodes, 65280 edges <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想知點樣有效 generate / eliminate"},{"pid":"e08c3bbf0f9eee34184b03b9b6818c1598d167bc","tid":2501263,"uid":121095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef8e6487a1fcd63021758c25f9b62b4713739149","tid":2501263,"uid":101554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:53:15.000Z","msg":"256 nodes, 65280 edges <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想知點樣有效 generate / eliminate"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:59:28.000Z","msg":"無咁多edges，估計應該得100條<br />\n因為restriction eliminate得好快 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c922d285451fbd69d8e26c943cf0610ae0e90ed","tid":2501263,"uid":147721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ef8e6487a1fcd63021758c25f9b62b4713739149","tid":2501263,"uid":101554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:53:15.000Z","msg":"256 nodes, 65280 edges <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想知點樣有效 generate / eliminate"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:00:38.000Z","msg":"你要eliminate啲nodes base on bits: 某啲bits唔可以同時係1/0<br />\n然後edges係dynamic gen: given node, get node with hamming distance &lt;= boat capacity (with additional constraints of node existence and boat location)<br />\nBtw佢個state係唔完整既 要有埋boat location"},{"pid":"25f78f08bc30eab8c280d8a6b2d398fa60cf9051","tid":2501263,"uid":147721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5b98e5f1d7de7dffe784b9300e3774b733b3ca24","tid":2501263,"uid":205339,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:50:35.000Z","msg":"痴撚線po"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:01:38.000Z","msg":"痴條毛 基本brute force"},{"pid":"086db49bb8ff67b6efc88e99420f85007a619b1b","tid":2501263,"uid":121095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:06:02.000Z","msg":"c++ code<br />\n<a href=\"http://cpp.sh/84bc3y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcpp.sh%2F84bc3y&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzi%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=88031ab6\" target=\"_blank\">http://cpp.sh/84bc3y</a>"},{"pid":"67c46851cc3c8c85707ad2d8e67afbafabb2a863","tid":2501263,"uid":10133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:06:12.000Z","msg":"本人弱智睇唔明"},{"pid":"fc85dfbcdfd67e6c129ac84b5cbf25ee02d705ae","tid":2501263,"uid":40684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:09:39.000Z","msg":"Use greedy la diu"},{"pid":"6948d7f9be0a6577c46999d032b4562f736e159e","tid":2501263,"uid":290080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:09:45.000Z","msg":"警察同犯走左就唔會返過黎，所以唔可以比佢地同時過到河對面，咁點計？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cdec70223f8eb506b49b5fc906e4a5f56bf6528","tid":2501263,"uid":121095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c922d285451fbd69d8e26c943cf0610ae0e90ed","tid":2501263,"uid":147721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ef8e6487a1fcd63021758c25f9b62b4713739149","tid":2501263,"uid":101554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:53:15.000Z","msg":"256 nodes, 65280 edges <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想知點樣有效 generate / eliminate"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:00:38.000Z","msg":"你要eliminate啲nodes base on bits: 某啲bits唔可以同時係1/0<br />\n然後edges係dynamic gen: given node, get node with hamming distance &lt;= boat capacity (with additional constraints of node existence and boat location)<br />\nBtw佢個state係唔完整既 要有埋boat location"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:10:24.000Z","msg":"ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一開始我就咁唔俾佢visit番visit過既state中左伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cross.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3ccdac17dd6ccc32d6b154a3bb7253765fec60a","tid":2501263,"uid":101554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:19:16.000Z","msg":"試下玩先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hair.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b3a024394e47df158b30f48decc358ba3ba715d","tid":2501263,"uid":134774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:22:53.000Z","msg":"講人話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b7e33969c633e8bd7ec7f97587f5b655ca241b4","tid":2501263,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:23:44.000Z","msg":"唔使搞到咁複雜<br />\n整白象子仔寫上名字和加唔可以一齊的用abcd來分類<br />\n真係好易"},{"pid":"0fa6483a70b55c01673384a57d6368fce9ba6b39","tid":2501263,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b7e33969c633e8bd7ec7f97587f5b655ca241b4","tid":2501263,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:23:44.000Z","msg":"唔使搞到咁複雜<br />\n整白象子仔寫上名字和加唔可以一齊的用abcd來分類<br />\n真係好易"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:24:47.000Z","msg":"更正<br />\n整8張紙仔寫上⋯"},{"pid":"8251beb6acf055d3b56f4edb2ceb2862d9510360","tid":2501263,"uid":121095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fa6483a70b55c01673384a57